 307:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @brief  Perform a mass erase or erase the specified FLASH memory pages with interrupt enabled
 308:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @note   To correctly run this function, the @ref HAL_FLASH_Unlock() function
 309:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         must be called before.
