 311:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         (recommended to protect the FLASH memory against possible unwanted operation)
 312:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @param  pEraseInit pointer to an FLASH_EraseInitTypeDef structure that
 313:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         contains the configuration information for the erasing.
 314:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *
 315:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL_StatusTypeDef HAL Status
 316:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   */
